snippet.title: Castle Doombad - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Watch the reveal trailer and prepare to become the villain in Castle Doombad, an upcoming expanded remake of 2014's dungeon-keeping strategy defense game coming to PC and Mac via Steam in 2023.
